180
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:53,160
 sam vodio na naftna polja u Kazahstani.

181
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:55,300
 I onda smo išli preko Moskve, Almate,

182
00:18:55,300 --> 00:18:57,440
 Atirau i Aktau.

183
00:18:57,440 --> 00:19:00,880
 I onda smo bili u Atirau na aerodromu,

184
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:03,040
