195
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:26,360
 oni ne dozvoljavaju ulozak u avioni.

196
00:19:26,360 --> 00:19:28,800
 Sad mi se smrzavamo na minus 15,

197
00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:30,260
 snijeg, ono, sve i nas,

198
00:19:30,260 --> 00:19:32,840
