 jak 40,

245
00:20:51,740 --> 00:20:52,680
 taj avion,

246
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:54,300
 točno se sjećam model aviona.

247
00:20:54,300 --> 00:20:55,400
 Ja vozim,

248
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,260
